query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 10 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-intent',
'asynchronous',
'authentication',
'cordova',
'dependency-injection',
'django-models',
'jsp',
'kotlin',
'mocking',
'opencv',
'pdf',
'sockets',
'spring-boot',
'visual-studio-2008',
'visual-studio-2013');
